jQuery News Ticker
-----------------------------------
	 	
An easy to use, slick and flexible news ticker in the style of the BBC News page ticker (http://news.bbc.co.uk).
	 	
Recommended for jQuery 1.4.x only (A very early version with support for with jQuery 1.3.2 is included, but is missing some features and will not be supported in future releases).	 	

Please visit http://www.jquerynewsticker.com/ for full documentation and downloads.
	 	
